** Vlad shook himself clean of dripping salt water, however, was soaked once again when Shesta decided to do the same. ** � Rotten creature!� ** He hissed in annoyance, turning a glare upon the dog. Shesta sank back and whimpered but Vlad took no notice, looking back at the Alliance Island he had escaped from with a grin.  Too soft, his mind computed before his optics focused upon the wilderness ahead of him, a planet full of life to be plundered but explored first of all.     Transforming into robot mode from beast, Vlad set his sights on the Maximal base as his destination. **
